---
title: Harissa Chicken Bulgur Bowls with Cilantro & Creamy Feta Sauce
description: We’re big fans of the ubiquitous grain bowl, but we have to admit: This one’s extra special. It’s a one-bowl feast that’s bursting with Middle Eastern–inspired flavors. The base is cucumber, tomato, scallions, cilantro, and feta with lemony bulgur—a hearty whole grain and longtime staple of Middle Eastern and Mediterranean cuisines. Topping the bowl—harissa-spiced chicken and a drizzle of creamy feta sauce. It doesn’t get much better than this!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6329e873eac2d9758e00ceda-d584d10a.jpg
